@startuml
autonumber
skinparam Style strictuml

actor "Người dùng" as User
participant "RegisterScreen" as FE
participant "AuthService (FE)" as AuthServiceFE
participant "AuthController" as Controller
participant "AuthService (BE)" as Service
participant "UserRepository" as Repo
participant "OtpService" as OtpSvc
participant "EmailService" as Email

User -> FE: Nhập (username, name, email, password)
FE -> FE: Tự validate (format email, độ dài pass)

FE -> AuthServiceFE: register(registerData)
note right: Chuyển data thành RegisterRequestDTO

AuthServiceFE -> Controller: POST /api/auth/register (DTO)
activate Controller

Controller -> Service: register(DTO)
activate Service

Service -> Repo: existsByUsername(DTO.username)
Service -> Repo: existsByEmail(DTO.email)

alt Email/Username đã tồn tại
    Service -> Controller: throw AlreadyExistsException
    Controller -> AuthServiceFE: 400 Bad Request (Error Response)
    AuthServiceFE -> FE: Hiển thị lỗi cho người dùng
else Thông tin hợp lệ
    Service -> Service: Hash password (BCrypt)

    par
        Service -> OtpSvc: savePendingRegistration(email, DTO)
    else
        Service -> OtpSvc: generateAndStoreOtp(email)
    end

    Service -> Email: sendOtpEmail(email, otp)

    Service -> Controller: Success Response ("OTP sent")
    deactivate Service

    Controller -> AuthServiceFE: 200 OK (ApiResponse)
    deactivate Controller

    AuthServiceFE -> FE: Trả về kết quả thành công
    FE -> User: Chuyển hướng sang trang Verify OTP
end
@enduml